<body>
	
<header>
	See if you can remember some things about the speaking section of the IELTS exam.Which of the following statements are true and which are false?
</header>
	
<section id="body">
  <img class="rightFloat" src="../media/TT_SP_003.jpg" mode="1" id="1001"/>
  
  <ol id="trueFalse">
  
    <li id="q1">The examiner asks all candidates the same questions. </li>
    <a id="a1"><b>True</b></a><tab/><a id="a2"><b>False</b></a>
    
    <li id="q2">The candidate has to state his or her full name. </li>
	<a id="a3"><b>True</b></a><tab/><a id="a4"><b>False</b></a>
    
    <li id="q3">All three parts of the test are connected to each other. </li>
	<a id="a5"><b>True</b></a><tab/><a id="a6"><b>False</b></a>
    
    <li id="q4">The candidate talks on his or her own about a topic of his choice. </li>
	<a id="a7"><b>True</b></a><tab/><a id="a8"><b>False</b></a>
    
    <li id="q5">The examiner introduces herself to the candidate. </li>
	<a id="a9"><b>True</b></a><tab/><a id="a10"><b>False</b></a>
    
    <li id="q6">The candidate has to produce identification. </li>
	<a id="a11"><b>True</b></a><tab/><a id="a12"><b>False</b></a>
    
    <li id="q7">The candidate has a turn to ask questions. </li>
	<a id="a13"><b>True</b></a><tab/><a id="a14"><b>False</b></a>
  </ol>
</section>

<section id="fb1">
  <p align="left">There are several different exam packs examiners can use and each has a variety of questions to choose from.</p>
</section>

<section id="fb2">
  <p align="left">Your name is needed for identification.</p>
</section>

<section id="fb3">
  <p align="left">Only Parts 2 and 3 are connected.</p>
</section>

<section id="fb4">
  <p align="left">The examiner will give you the topic to talk about.</p>
</section>

<section id="fb5">
  <p align="left">Examiners will introduce themselves.</p>
</section>

<section id="fb6">
  <p align="left">Without identification you will not be allowed to take the exam.</p>
</section>

<section id="fb7">
  <p align="left">The candidate can ask for a question to be repeated or clarified but nothing else.</p>
</section>

